      +- Release Information -+

        Smart protection against spam and malware

        Defend your organization against spam, viruses, spyware, malicious
        web sites, and inappropriate surfing with an affordable and
        simple-to-manage hardware or virtual appliance. Whether you have
        50 employees or thousands, it's a smart email and web security
        solution. Integrated protection safeguards you more effectively
        against threats from email and the web, while reducing complexity
        and cost.


